     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "C - Si le r\u00e9sultat est sup\u00e9rieur \u00e0 48 dents, plus d'un tour a \u00e9t\u00e9 effectu\u00e9 ; recommencer \u00e0 l'\u00e9tape 1",
